{"tid":1459864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［輸出革命］張黑講成白 白講成黑","createTime":"2019-08-12T23:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T01:15:44.000Z","uid":70609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb1459c5eec81e6757330d0d4915827883ebab7","tid":1459864,"uid":70609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:05:18.000Z","msg":"聽完眾巴打講文宣正確方向後<br />\n<br />\n我媽媽經歷過文化大革命，有少少野想同大家講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456583</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我有個idea<br />\n我地可以將黑講成白 白講成黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然政府將示威者沫黑成暴徒<br />\n我地都可以將示威者講成係愛國愛黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地可以將示威者描述成愛國愛黨<br />\n而事實都係咁<br />\n我地要&lsquo;保住&rsquo;香港關係法<br />\n而政府哩家嘅所作所為正正就係破壞緊香港關係法<br />\n當中最重要嘅係錢<br />\n因為支那人眼中只有錢<br />\n我地可以攞住哩個point 作為文宣向中国人宣傳<br />\n因為支那人最鍾意愛國愛黨哩4個字<br />\n我自己係外國讀書 都有啲支那朋友<br />\n我試過用以上嘅point 同佢地講<br />\n佢地聽完之後確實有動搖過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有用 大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\nPs 光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28994b492e4ff10ee965a1c3de9298ad9edce23c","tid":1459864,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:54:11.000Z","msg":"去示威時拎住國旗。上腦的人會忌三分。<br />\n樣樣嘢拉去&ldquo;外國勢力&rdquo;&ldquo;愛國&rdquo;&ldquo;民族&rdquo;"},{"pid":"0a0e70bca49e53667d73311d73b6f70b2b944688","tid":1459864,"uid":296222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:54:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2006bca19e3beb513162dd74bb3976a9e9c1939","tid":1459864,"uid":70609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:08:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4b07ca298ec98706aae011cd3920bbcd0902e4ad","tid":1459864,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:09:21.000Z","msg":"【打夠飛機未】「勝利」既背後 係一場恐慌式既撤退<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459738</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2ed6686dc53c5b900194a4fffeab0056798ca08b","tid":1459864,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正咩野都有 唔差在<br />\n<br />\n等d資訊更加料"},{"pid":"dd0d25d06427e21b1d2b4b530bd91938382a9878","tid":1459864,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:15:44.000Z","msg":"[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n幫手支持廣獨，將革命思想傳入中國！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nZFbOE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nZFbOE.png&h=4fd8318f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打可以用下面條link去印，set左a5 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=52740830\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR</a>"}]}